BeautyBox Marketplace Project Prompt

Create a modern, responsive web application called BeautyBox Marketplace.

Project Description

BeautyBox Marketplace is an online marketplace that connects customers with beauty and cosmetic product sellers. The platform should allow customers to browse products, search for items, add products to a shopping cart, place orders, and leave reviews. Sellers should be able to manage products, inventory, and customer orders through a dedicated dashboard.

The application should be beginner-friendly, secure, responsive, and suitable for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.

User Roles
1. Customer

Customers should be able to:

Register an account
Login and logout
Edit profile information
Browse all products
Search products by name
Filter products by category
View product details
Add products to cart
Update cart quantities
Remove products from cart
Place orders
View order history
Track order status
Leave ratings and reviews
2. Seller

Sellers should be able to:

Register seller account
Login and logout
Manage profile
Add new products
Edit products
Delete products
Upload product images
Manage inventory
View customer orders
Update order status
View sales statistics
3. Admin

Admins should be able to:

Manage users
Manage sellers
Manage products
Manage categories
View marketplace statistics
Manage reviews
Suspend or delete accounts
Monitor orders
